<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Health Quiz | MediConnect</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/quiz.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Health Quiz</h1>
        <p>Test your general health awareness!</p>
        <form id="quizForm">
            <div class="quiz-item">
                <p>1. What is the normal body temperature in Fahrenheit?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="a"> 97.0°F</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="b"> 98.6°F</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="c"> 100.2°F</label>
            </div>
            <div class="quiz-item">
                <p>2. What vitamin is produced when the skin is exposed to sunlight?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="a"> Vitamin A</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="b"> Vitamin D</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q2" value="c"> Vitamin C</label>
            </div>
            <div class="quiz-item">
                <p>3. Which organ purifies blood in the human body?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="a"> Liver</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="b"> Kidney</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q3" value="c"> Heart</label>
            </div>
            <div class="quiz-item">
                <p>4. How much of the human body is made up of water?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="a"> 50-55%</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="b"> 60-70%</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q4" value="c"> 80-85%</label>
            </div>
            <div class="quiz-item">
                <p>5. Which of the following is considered a "good" cholesterol?</p>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="a"> LDL</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="b"> HDL</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="q5" value="c"> VLDL</label>
            </div>
            <button type="button" onclick="submitQuiz()">Submit</button>
        </form>
        <div id="result"></div>
    </div>
    <script src="/js/quiz.js"></script>
</body>
</html>